+/- : Zoom in/out
a : Autoscale
w : Fit to width
h : Fit to height
j/k : Pan down/up
f/m : flip/mirror
r/R : Rotate (Clock wise and ant-clock wise)
ESC/q : Quit
#+END_SRC
